<p class="document-bullet">**Deadline for Response:**</p><p class="document-signature">You are required to respond to this letter within 7 days of receipt, providing a satisfactory resolution to this matter. If I do not receive a satisfactory response by [Deadline Date: 2025-04-22], I will escalate this issue to Consumer Affairs Victoria and consider further action through the Victorian Civil and Administrative Tribunal (VCAT).</p><p class="document-paragraph">Please consider this an opportunity to resolve this matter amicably and avoid further legal proceedings.</p><p class="document-paragraph">Yours sincerely,</p><p class="document-signature">[Signature]</p><p class="document-paragraph">awdawd  </p><p class="document-bullet">---</p><p class="document-paragraph">Please ensure that this letter is printed on your personal or business letterhead if available, and sent via a method that provides proof of delivery, such as registered post. This will provide evidence of your attempt to resolve the matter should further action be necessary.</p>
    
